of connection and community?

308
00:14:39.086 --> 00:14:40.463
Yes, that's why I'm here.

309
00:14:40.505 --> 00:14:43.007
Yeah, I'm not one
of those monsters.

310
00:14:43.049 --> 00:14:44.884
So please,
keep to your side of the room

311
00:14:44.925 --> 00:14:49.263
and I won't have
to suck all your blood out.

312
00:14:49.305 --> 00:14:52.475
And no garlic,
even garlic powder or anchovies

313
00:14:52.517 --> 00:14:54.561
because they're gross.

314
00:14:55.186 --> 00:14:57.104
She's fun.

315
00:14:57.146 --> 00:14:59.607
I'm not even sure I have blood.

316
00:15:00.316 --> 00:15:02.569
Well, first day
of class tomorrow.

317
00:15:02.610 --> 00:15:06.447
I'm all charged up,
or I will be.

318
00:15:06.823 --> 00:15:09.659
[electricity zapping]

319
00:15:09.701 --> 00:15:13.162
[soft music]

320
00:15:14.038 --> 00:15:16.040
[Dad] <i>Remember,
the school is serious</i>

321
00:15:16.082 --> 00:15:18.376
<i>about keeping humans out.</i>

322
00:15:18.418 --> 00:15:21.755
<i>♪♪</i>

323
00:15:26.593 --> 00:15:29.470
[woman over PA] <i>Good morning,
Monster High!</i>

324
00:15:29.512 --> 00:15:31.514
<i>Classes begin today.</i>

325
00:15:31.556 --> 00:15:36.018
<i>A reminder to all amphibious
students to hydrate often.</i>

326
00:15:36.060 --> 00:15:37.729
[bell ringing]

327
00:15:37.771 --> 00:15:39.980
I can't believe it, school!

328
00:15:40.022 --> 00:15:42.024
Here we are,
walking down a hallway

329
00:15:42.066 --> 00:15:44.985
with other kids
like in the movies.

330
00:15:45.027 --> 00:15:46.987
This is so cool, Frankie.

331
00:15:47.029 --> 00:15:49.198
This is all very confusing.

332
00:15:49.240 --> 00:15:51.075
Most of my human parts
were self-taught

333
00:15:51.117 --> 00:15:52.619
