before schools existed.

334
00:15:52.660 --> 00:15:54.704
Am I walking right,
high school-ish?

335
00:15:54.746 --> 00:15:56.664
What kind of movies did you
watch to prepare for this?

336
00:15:56.706 --> 00:16:00.251
Also, what's a movie?

337
00:16:00.293 --> 00:16:02.879
Cool, these are our lockers.

338
00:16:02.921 --> 00:16:05.214
<i>♪ 'Cause this is who I am
This is who I am ♪</i>

339
00:16:05.256 --> 00:16:07.634
I cannot wait to decorate mine.

340
00:16:07.675 --> 00:16:10.261
<i>♪ Someone
Who can understand ♪</i>

341
00:16:10.303 --> 00:16:12.680
I'm so happy
we're locker buddies.

342
00:16:12.722 --> 00:16:14.933
<i>♪ 'Cause I can be
My true self, yeah ♪</i>

343
00:16:14.974 --> 00:16:17.852
Look! How fun is that?

344
00:16:17.894 --> 00:16:20.772
A vending machine
with, like, snacks.

345
00:16:22.440 --> 00:16:24.525
Jellied Newt Eyeballs,

346
00:16:24.567 --> 00:16:28.070
okay, not my jam, but still fun.

347
00:16:28.112 --> 00:16:30.573
Look alive, ghouls.

348
00:16:30.615 --> 00:16:32.158
[pounds]

349
00:16:32.199 --> 00:16:35.244
<i>♪♪</i>

350
00:16:35.286 --> 00:16:36.746
[both] Wow.

351
00:16:36.788 --> 00:16:38.456
- Hey, broski.
- Hey, man.

352
00:16:38.498 --> 00:16:40.040
What's going on?

353
00:16:40.082 --> 00:16:41.751
Lagoona, how do I look?

354
00:16:41.793 --> 00:16:44.128
As spooktastic as always.

355
00:16:44.170 --> 00:16:45.713
Knew it.

356
00:16:46.464 --> 00:16:48.257
Hey, Deuce.

357
00:16:48.299 --> 00:16:49.843
Hey, Cleo.

358
00:16:49.884 --> 00:16:53.387
Your hair is fire, Heath.

359
00:16:53.429 --> 00:16:55.640
Thanks, totally ignited
my pillow this morning.

360
00:16:55.682 --> 00:16:57.099
Smelled like burnt cheese.

361
00:16:57.141 --> 00:16:59.435
It wasn't a compliment.
It's scorching my gauze.

362
00:16:59.477 --> 00:17:01.145
Please step back.

363
00:17:01.187 --> 00:17:03.481
Happy to.

364
00:17:03.523 --> 00:17:05.024
What's up?

365
00:17:05.065 --> 00:17:06.985
Oh, I just wanted to say

366
00:17:07.026 --> 00:17:09.654
I'm officially totally good
with our breakup.

367
00:17:09.696 --> 00:17:11.739
Fabulous, actually.

368
00:17:11.781 --> 00:17:14.033
I have a long list
of other interested creatures

369
00:17:14.074 --> 00:17:15.952
just waiting to date me.

370
00:17:15.994 --> 00:17:17.829
It's good to see
that you've moved on, Cleo,

371
00:17:17.871 --> 00:17:20.039
and that you're still
the same impressively

372
00:17:20.080 --> 00:17:22.333
self-involved monster
I broke up with.

373
00:17:22.375 --> 00:17:24.043
Hey, Heath, wait up, man.

374
00:17:24.084 --> 00:17:26.295
He totally wants you back.

375
00:17:28.548 --> 00:17:30.424
Check out
the walking jigsaw puzzle.

376
00:17:30.466 --> 00:17:32.134
Hi, I'm Frankie.

377
00:17:32.176 --> 00:17:34.220
I'm made from a collection
of dead people's body parts.

378
00:17:34.261 --> 00:17:36.180
And that hair, there's a reason

379
00:17:36.222 --> 00:17:37.932
