410
00:18:51.839 --> 00:18:55.760
Ooh, the headmistress,
she is so terrifying.

411
00:18:55.802 --> 00:18:58.471
<i>I said Clawdeen Wolf,
to the headmistress's office!</i>

412
00:18:58.512 --> 00:19:01.599
- I got this.
- Cool.

413
00:19:01.641 --> 00:19:04.560
- [clock chiming]
- [screaming]

414
00:19:06.896 --> 00:19:09.774
[deep growling]

415
00:19:16.656 --> 00:19:20.409
